commit.message: mainApp must be configured in servlet
write more information about binaries into response
set cache-control if not in development mode
don't add classLoader to context in production mode
do an environment lookup for resource
look for resource "jdbc/linch" instead of creating own datasource
add datasource to container only if it exists
removed dependency to linch-apps; loading linch-app-properties, linch-db-properties and linch-components-properties
moved dynamic class loader to linch-dev
simplified production and development invocation; renamed system property to com.linchproject.dev
dynamic class loader loads resources from source
added a dynamic class loader that compiles classes on every request when environment is set to development
implemented session service and cookie service
register apps in classpath and load components
user id is stored and read from http session
renamed req and resp to request and response
made renderer configurable via init parameter
